Source: shaka-lab-gateway-client
Maintainer: Joey Parrish <joeyparrish@google.com>
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Standards-Version: 3.9.2
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9)

Package: shaka-lab-gateway-client
Architecture: all
Depends: libnss-ldapd
Description: Shaka Lab Gateway Client
 Allows Active Directory users from Shaka Lab Gateway to log in.
 .
 **NOTE**: Exactly one Linux device on your lab network must install the
 shaka-lab-gateway package.  Devices with the client package will connect to
 that gateway.
